    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Windshield, and Windshield Wipers</title>
        <para>The BE Series school bus utilizes a large three piece windshield assembly allowing the driver a full
            unobstructed field of view. The windshield wipers are designed to allow for the largest windshield cleaning
            area available on the conventional class school bus in the industry. The wiper pattern allows for a larger
            field of vision during inclement weather operation.
        </para>
